{
  "$schema": "https://gobl.org/draft-0/tax/addon-def",
  "key": "fr-ctc-flow6-v1",
  "name": {
    "en": "France CTC Flow 6 (Cycle de Vie)",
    "fr": "France CTC Flux 6 (Cycle de Vie)"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Support for Flow 6 (\"Cycle de Vie\") lifecycle status\nmessages of the French CTC reform. Carries the CDAR\nProcessConditionCode on bill.Status documents exchanged\nbetween registered dematerialisation platforms (PDPs)\nand the Portail Public de Facturation (PPF).",
    "fr": "Support du Flux 6 (« Cycle de Vie ») de la réforme\nfrançaise CTC. Porte le ProcessConditionCode CDAR sur\nles documents bill.Status échangés entre les plateformes\nde dématérialisation agréées (PDP) et le Portail Public\nde Facturation (PPF)."
  },
  "sources": [
    {
      "title": {
        "en": "External Specifications",
        "fr": "Spécifications Externes"
      },
      "url": "https://www.impots.gouv.fr/specifications-externes-b2b"
    }
  ],
