      "key": "fr-ctc-flow6-role",
      "name": {
        "en": "Party Role Code",
        "fr": "Code rôle partie"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "UNCL 3035 role code carried as the CDAR RoleCode (MDT-158)\non each populated party of any Flow 6 lifecycle message\n— set on Supplier / Customer of both bill.Status and\nbill.Payment. Labels follow the French CTC\nspecification, which assigns CDAR-specific meanings to\nWK (dematerialisation platform / operator) and DFH\n(Portail Public de Facturation). The normalizer fills\nthe obvious defaults (Supplier → SE, Customer → BY)\nand leaves the rest for the caller to set explicitly."
      },
