    {
      "key": "fr-ctc-flow6-condition",
      "name": {
        "en": "Flow 6 Condition Code",
        "fr": "Code condition Flux 6"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "CDAR CharacteristicTypeCode (MDT-207). Unified\nvocabulary; the rules narrow the allow-list per\ndocument type:\n\n  - On bill.Reason under bill.Status: CBB, DIV, DVA,\n    MAJ (field-level corrections), MAP / MAPTTC /\n    MNA / MNATTC (partial-approval / rejection\n    amounts), ESC / RAB / REM (discount markers).\n    Each Reason carries 0..1 condition (CDAR\n    cardinality); to convey multiple characteristics\n    for the same status line, add multiple Reasons.\n    bill.Condition entries on each Reason are reserved\n    for Peppol cac:Condition-style business-rule\n    codes describing the affected field and value.\n  - On bill.Payment.Ext: MEN (Encaissé), MPA (Payé),\n    RAP (Reste à payer). The normalizer defaults the\n    value from bill.Payment.Type (receipt → MEN,\n    advice → MPA); partial payments can override to\n    RAP."
      },
      "values": [
        {
          "code": "CBB",
          "name": {
            "en": "Bank details to modify",
            "fr": "Coordonnées bancaires à modifier"
          }
        },
        {
          "code": "DIV",
