    {
      "key": "fr-ctc-flow6-action",
      "name": {
        "en": "Flow 6 Action Code",
        "fr": "Code action Flux 6"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "CDAR RequestedActionCode (MDT-121) carried on a\nbill.Action under a bill.Status line. Tells the issuer\nwhat to do next with the referenced invoice — reissue\nit, send a credit note, provide more information, etc.\nThe normalizer derives the default from bill.Action.Key\n(NOA / PIN / NIN / CNF / CNP / CNA / OTH);\ncallers can override directly on the extension when\nround-tripping a parsed CDV."
      },
      "values": [
